<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1940-03-15T18:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1940-03-15T18:00:00-05:00" n="901" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d901">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">867.5151/177: Telegram</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Turkey</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">MacMurray</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                </hi>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Ankara</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1940-03-16T01:00:00+02:00">March
                                        16, 1940—1 a.m.</date>
                                    <lb/> [Received 3:51 p.m.]</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>28. My telegram No. 19, March 5, 4 p.m., from Istanbul [<hi rend="italic">Ankara</hi>]. Exchange Office there [Istanbul]
                                advises that up to March 15 exchange permits issued since the
                                resumption of exchange transfers on March 4 total $287,400.
                                Transfers leave [<hi rend="italic">have?</hi>] now been effected on
                                all applications filed prior to July 1, 1939.</p>
                            <p>Total unpaid applications for exchange transfer permits on file as of
                                March 14 amount to $4,680,000.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">MacMurray</hi>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>